{"tid":1637070,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸出生，香港永久居民，第一次入台，張入台証係咪要特別去邊到整？","createTime":"2019-10-08T01:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T08:37:29.000Z","uid":260328,"like":14,"dislike":432,"uniUserReply":123,"replies":[{"pid":"bcc9f8d8d2807962abb21296a9588d0c7eedfdbf","tid":1637070,"uid":260328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:24:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小妹大陸出世既，3-4歲黎左香港，<br />\n<br />\n黎緊就會同朋友去畢業旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小妹第一次去台灣，咁岩成班fd skype起就咁岩講到入台証啲野，有個fd就提一提我，話佢呀媽大陸出世 之前第一次去台灣，張入台証要特別去個地方搞，唔可以上網搞，但細節佢又唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想問一問大家，知唔知大陸出生既永久居民既入台証要點樣搞 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1811c44dc2411293cf581c9fe732977bcffa46b2","tid":1637070,"uid":1550,"like":141,"dislike":1,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:26:02.000Z","msg":"咁大個人google都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86506e77b0b389d15e0ad7f15127716e0fca65b7","tid":1637070,"uid":61416,"like":103,"dislike":67,"score":36,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:26:20.000Z","msg":"大陸喱緊係番大陸整"},{"pid":"0da3bbd6358a86e81f14e100dae9d0285e1acd33","tid":1637070,"uid":66719,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:26:28.000Z","msg":"去金鐘帶相填表"},{"pid":"ddb3adfa85e2254fae04924ebb6e4b6e8cbbbd85","tid":1637070,"uid":166908,"like":31,"dislike":10,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:27:48.000Z","msg":"臭G連自己百度都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83e6aeafa843e580c8affbef4a0ac718ea4c114","tid":1637070,"uid":297750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:27:56.000Z","msg":"可以網上搞 但係要填detail d果份表"},{"pid":"c3f78e4fc23f8b38dfeded81ad54f0e9bee4461b","tid":1637070,"uid":326966,"like":17,"dislike":59,"score":-42,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:28:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e9068d46e9f367c7d4666147e2b753d5886e93c","tid":1637070,"uid":221360,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:29:14.000Z","msg":"第一次要去金鐘填表申請，帶相帶passport"},{"pid":"84ff88ad37c0aacde5d05dcd123a6cab4f6a10eb","tid":1637070,"uid":202989,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:29:37.000Z","msg":"其實你google 會快過係到等巴絲覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55076633712ce854031ef990c092886d7a5c2d37","tid":1637070,"uid":221360,"like":75,"dislike":18,"score":57,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:30:47.000Z","msg":"連登真係多左好多無腦撚，一聽到大陸出世都要屌兩屌，一係五毛一係屎忽生上腦"},{"pid":"a158b30e742fb17b4587dd9316a2f0ce87d1e877","tid":1637070,"uid":226594,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:30:52.000Z","msg":"(1) 非香港出生＋首次去台灣<br />\n*適用於持有香港特區護照或BNO護照、而又未持有其他國家護照的申請者<br />\n<br />\n非香港出生之香港永久性居民（持香港特區護照或BNO護照，未持有其他國家護照者）首次前往台灣，遊客需要利用雲端線上申請台灣簽證。申請網址是：<br />\n<a href=\"https://coa.immigration.gov.tw/coa-frontend/overseas-honk-macao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcoa.immigration.gov.tw%2Fcoa-frontend%2Foverseas-honk-macao&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnImVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=32781eb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://coa.immigration.gov.tw/coa-frontend/overseas-honk-macao</a><br />\n申請時需準備：<br />\n<br />\n最近2年內拍攝之2吋半身彩色白底照片１張(照片規格請參考注意事項)，上傳相片檔案格式須為JPG或JPEG檔，相片圖檔檔案大小需在512KB以內。<br />\n香港永久性居民身分證、有效期3個月以上之香港護照或BNO護照、及回鄉證影本。<br />\n證照費：單次入出境證：新臺幣600元整；一年多次入出境證：新臺幣1000元整；三年多次入出境證：新臺幣2000元整。"},{"pid":"f804d8d032487259934e4d70856d5156a2cef3ad","tid":1637070,"uid":260328,"like":88,"dislike":6,"score":82,"quote":{"pid":"86506e77b0b389d15e0ad7f15127716e0fca65b7","tid":1637070,"uid":61416,"like":103,"dislike":67,"score":36,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:26:20.000Z","msg":"大陸喱緊係番大陸整"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:32:06.000Z","m