,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:30:22.000Z","msg":"返鄉下攪"},{"pid":"0dac61364b50a0334b24134d9db264fc9038c8e2","tid":1637070,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcc9f8d8d2807962abb21296a9588d0c7eedfdbf","tid":1637070,"uid":260328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:24:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小妹大陸出世既，3-4歲黎左香港，<br />\n<br />\n黎緊就會同朋友去畢業旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小妹第一次去台灣，咁岩成班fd skype起就咁岩講到入台証啲野，有個fd就提一提我，話佢呀媽大陸出世 之前第一次去台灣，張入台証要特別去個地方搞，唔可以上網搞，但細節佢又唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想問一問大家，知唔知大陸出生既永久居民既入台証要點樣搞 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:31:39.000Z","msg":"其實你唔嫌貴 可以搵旅行社搞<br />\n上網搞好煩<br />\nUpload相又要scan <br />\n整唔到又要重新整過<br />\n未反送中嗰陣去左中旅搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢價錢最平<br />\n300幾<br />\n其他 康泰嗰d 都500-600<br />\n好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：幾個月已經係香港 雖然唔係香港出世 但對香港已經有歸屬感 遊行都去左10幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd9aa5e639256418757067de211f3a91643ef52","tid":1637070,"uid":203397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:33:20.000Z","msg":"Dna真係咁難擺脫？"},{"pid":"9c1580f42f7bdb69426f8ae0e41f2008cbd0b2ac","tid":1637070,"uid":196485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"9d73f1381f1a1538b3441f4f458a357497a89703","tid":1637070,"uid":197256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:35:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支那人 你有咩資格去台灣? 死返上大灣區啦</span>"},{"pid":"6ddd2a105fbaafe069ae59c720cf0da671f9acc1","tid":1637070,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco